2
00:00:06,573 --> 00:00:08,823
Unlimited space.
Boundless suffering for the fallen souls

3
00:00:10,010 --> 00:00:11,910
Uninterrupted time

4
00:00:13,914 --> 00:00:14,904
Time

5
00:00:15,482 --> 00:00:17,002
I still remember my first arrest

6
00:00:18,051 --> 00:00:19,801
Year: 1991

7
00:00:20,254 --> 00:00:22,334
It was December 12, 1980

8
00:00:26,193 --> 00:00:28,333
My partner and I were patrolling Hano Road

9
00:00:29,663 --> 00:00:32,593
Shit was going down at New World Centre

10
00:00:33,267 --> 00:00:34,637
We rushed over

11
00:00:35,602 --> 00:00:38,352
A gang fight was taking place

12
00:00:39,039 --> 00:00:41,259
About fifteen or so were already down

13
00:00:42,709 --> 00:00:43,939
Lots of blood on the ground

14
00:00:45,913 --> 00:00:47,903
Plus a severed hand, still holding a knife

15
00:00:53,921 --> 00:00:55,381
My partner told me to draw my piece

16
00:00:56,757 --> 00:00:59,797
I was a rookie so ! did what he told

17
00:01:01,695 --> 00:01:03,565
But before I could open the holster

18
00:01:04,063 --> 00:01:06,874
My partner already dropped

19
00:01:08,135 --> 00:01:12,205
This kid stabbed a pipe into his belly

20
00:01:13,707 --> 00:01:16,336
Blood gushed out of the sawed-off opening

21
00:01:18,645 --> 00:01:20,455
I didn't know what to think

22
00:01:21,014 --> 00:01:22,154
I simply put all six of my bullets

23
00:01:22,616 --> 00:01:24,866
straight into that kid!

24
00:01:27,254 --> 00:01:29,744
I don't remember how many years he got

25
00:01:31,725 --> 00:01:33,975
But when I saw him again two years ago

26
00:01:34,928 --> 00:01:38,178
he was boozing in a club, looking sharp

27
00:01:38,999 --> 00:01:42,189
His buddies were all Kwun's goons!

28
00:01:46,607 --> 00:01:50,737
Evil prevails. Only the good die young

29
00:01:57,718 --> 00:01:59,768
I can barely recall my partner's face now

30
00:02:01,822 --> 00:02:02,932
l regret

31
00:02:03,924 --> 00:02:06,674
The six bullets weren't put into that kid's skull

32
00:02:13,634 --> 00:02:15,333
The world shouldn't be like this

33
00:02:17,137 --> 00:02:18,977
It's not the way to be, Sam

34
00:02:26,613 --> 00:02:27,693
How long have you been around Tsim Sha Tsui?

35
00:02:29,583 --> 00:02:30,693
Almost two years now

36
00:02:33,920 --> 00:02:35,730
Do you know why I haven't messed with you?

37
00:02:37,257 --> 00:02:38,397
‘Cause I am handsome!

38
00:02:40,127 --> 00:02:41,417
Maybe so

39
00:02:43,230 --> 00:02:44,899
‘Cause I think you're a decent guy

40
00:02:47,901 --> 00:02:51,381
I'd rather you be in charge

41
00:02:52,239 --> 00:02:53,059
Forget about it

42
00:02:53,807 --> 00:02:55,587
You couldn't waste the kid even with six bullets

43
00:02:56,176 --> 00:02:57,576
That makes you a decent guy, too. Right?

44
00:02:58,645 --> 00:03:02,245
I don't want to be one

45
00:03:09,956 --> 00:03:12,585
Kwun gave me everything, even my life

46
00:03:13,894 --> 00:03:17,324
If! turned against him

47
00:03:17,964 --> 00:03:19,714
I'd be despicable even in your eyes. Right?

48
00:03:22,269 --> 00:03:24,549
I knew you'd say that

49
00:03:26,940 --> 00:03:30,400
Chivalry means little to the Ngai Family

50
00:03:36,583 --> 00:03:37,923
The Master often says

51
00:03:39,252 --> 00:03:41,712
Retribution knows its time

52
00:03:44,157 --> 00:03:47,287
Who knows how you and I will end up?

53
00:03:51,598 --> 00:03:52,528
Time to work!

54
00:03:54,000 --> 00:03:56,310
This early?

55
00:03:57,003 --> 00:03:58,373
I've got to eat! So do my boys!

56
00:03:58,872 --> 00:04:00,012
Take the whole box

57
00:04:00,607 --> 00:04:01,457
That's okay. Keep it

58
00:04:01,875 --> 00:04:03,365
Don't worry about it! Just go!

59
00:04:12,185 --> 00:04:13,675
Want to use the back door?

60
00:04:14,755 --> 00:04:17,385
Ain't no rules against schmoozing with cops

61
00:04:18,524 --> 00:04:20,255
The front door's fine. Got used to it

62
00:04:37,077 --> 00:04:37,927
Prat Avenue!

63
00:05:00,000 --> 00:05:01,370
Prat Avenue

64
00:06:31,091 --> 00:06:32,051
Is Uncle Kwun in?

65
00:06:33,994 --> 00:06:35,634
Uncle Kwun! Someone's looking for you!

66
00:07:32,752 --> 00:07:33,682
Bye, Mary

67
00:07:49,035 --> 00:07:50,615
They say this American antique's got...

68
00:07:51,004 --> 00:07:54,664
..sweet high, crisp middle and strong bass

69
00:07:55,909 --> 00:07:57,399
Bullshit!

70
00:07:58,178 --> 00:07:59,438
180 grand!

71
00:07:59,813 --> 00:08:01,832
Who can afford it in Hong Kong?

72
00:08:02,615 --> 00:08:03,465
Sit

73
00:08:07,654 --> 00:08:09,734
Only around ten thousand people can afford it

74
00:08:10,557 --> 00:08:12,487
Sam asked you to be a mole in the force

75
00:08:13,493 --> 00:08:15,953
If you don't like it, [ can talk to him

76
00:08:16,663 --> 00:08:17,923
You're my boy after all

77
00:08:21,001 --> 00:08:21,760
It's fine with me

78
00:08:23,503 --> 00:08:24,433
Sure?

79
00:08:26,172 --> 00:08:27,162
Positive

80
00:08:30,510 --> 00:08:31,650
Hand me that bag

81
00:08:35,482 --> 00:08:36,182
Mary

82
00:08:38,684 --> 00:08:41,645
[ thought you'd been dreading it

83
00:08:43,089 --> 00:08:46,129
Hide in Tuen Mun till things quiet down

84
00:08:46,926 --> 00:08:48,856
Stay fit for the Academy's new term

85
00:08:52,132 --> 00:08:54,561
The money ! gave you, spend wisely

86
00:08:58,638 --> 00:08:59,598
You like the song?

87
00:09:01,808 --> 00:09:02,658
Yeah

88
00:09:08,281 --> 00:09:09,420
It's yours

89
00:09:10,250 --> 00:09:12,590
It won't sound as good on another player

90
00:09:13,920 --> 00:09:16,610
Someday I'll pick out a good one for you

91
00:09:19,292 --> 00:09:21,252
What? Don't like it?

92
00:09:23,063 --> 00:09:23,963
Not at all

93
00:09:24,731 --> 00:09:26,431
Sam gave you this watch, didn't he?

94
00:09:27,033 --> 00:09:28,053
None of your business

95
00:09:35,075 --> 00:09:36,365
Only you and I...

96
00:09:37,310 --> 00:09:38,680
..know about tonight

97
00:09:39,646 --> 00:09:40,786
I don't want Sam to know

98
00:09:42,048 --> 00:09:42,978
Why's that?

99
00:09:44,717 --> 00:09:46,357
Women are simple

100
00:09:47,487 --> 00:09:50,507
A man treats me well, I'd do anything

101
00:09:53,259 --> 00:09:56,719
Now go home. I'm very busy tonight

102
00:10:09,209 --> 00:10:13,598
It's either you or me

103
00:10:14,614 --> 00:10:18,184
The boss said I would see blood today

104
00:10:20,086 --> 00:10:22,636
The Mainlander kept asking...

105
00:10:23,256 --> 00:10:24,986
Got a Mercedes today, Keung?

106
00:10:25,658 --> 00:10:27,678
l said, "Of course." And here I am!

107
00:10:28,595 --> 00:10:31,555
Otherwise, I wouldn't be here with you

108
00:10:32,265 --> 00:10:36,185
Mainland girls in arms

109
00:10:36,970 --> 00:10:37,990
That's for sure!

110
00:10:44,043 --> 00:10:45,773
Hey, got a cigarette?

111
00:10:47,280 --> 00:10:48,480
I don't smoke

112
00:11:03,630 --> 00:11:05,680
Let's forget about it. My car's fine

113
00:11:06,166 --> 00:11:08,386
See! She says it's all good

114
00:11:09,969 --> 00:11:11,989
Dressed all dandy

115
00:11:12,705 --> 00:11:15,695
Don't want any trouble, do you?

116
00:11:16,643 --> 00:11:18,813
Look at me. All beaten up by you

117
00:11:19,646 --> 00:11:22,805
Who do you think the judge would believe?

118
00:11:24,050 --> 00:11:27,150
bet you guys never go to Tsim Sha Tsui East, huh?

119
00:11:27,787 --> 00:11:29,807
Know who I am? I'm Keung!

120
00:11:30,590 --> 00:11:32,870
Sam's top dog. Del Piero's boy

121
00:11:33,560 --> 00:11:35,670
I'll kick your ass every time I see you

122
00:11:36,229 --> 00:11:37,099
And you can count on that

123
00:11:59,085 --> 00:12:00,955
How about calling an ambulance, sir?

124
00:12:01,588 --> 00:12:02,928
Look at all the blood!

125
00:12:03,756 --> 00:12:05,776
Have them bring 500 cc Type O. It's rare!

126
00:12:06,192 --> 00:12:07,092
Shut up!

127
00:12:07,660 --> 00:12:09,329
Wait till we're back to the station

128
00:12:11,598 --> 00:12:13,027
Why do I have to go to the station?

129
00:12:13,933 --> 00:12:15,103
l only stole a piece of junk, sir!

130
00:12:15,835 --> 00:12:16,505
What've I done to deserve the OCTB?

131
00:12:16,836 --> 00:12:17,186
Just shut up!

132
00:12:17,637 --> 00:12:17,957
Does that deserve an OCTB beating?

133
00:12:18,271 --> 00:12:19,940
Don't you know you're just a cadet?

134
00:12:21,040 --> 00:12:23,260
And you are expected to get a medal this year

135
00:12:24,143 --> 00:12:25,433
Don't ever let Yip know about this!

136
00:12:37,690 --> 00:12:38,680
Happy birthday!

137
00:12:39,025 --> 00:12:40,775
What's there to be happy about?

138
00:12:41,561 --> 00:12:44,661
Ten years in the Academy. A rustic hell

139
00:12:47,900 --> 00:12:49,100
You even managed to get me out

140
00:12:49,636 --> 00:12:51,305
Your case's now ancient history

141
00:12:51,738 --> 00:12:54,198
Get yourself out

142
00:12:56,643 --> 00:12:58,983
So what if the Commissioner's Chinese now?

143
00:12:59,746 --> 00:13:01,856
Still six more years till the hand-over

144
00:13:02,615 --> 00:13:04,425
I'll be 48 by then!

145
00:13:05,818 --> 00:13:10,098
Might as well train a few good cops here!

146
00:13:11,591 --> 00:13:13,781
The world is yours after 1997!

147
00:13:15,728 --> 00:13:17,397
27149! Cheers!

148
00:13:19,098 --> 00:13:19,858
Yan

149
00:13:20,233 --> 00:13:21,083
Been beeping the whole day

150
00:13:21,601 --> 00:13:21,981
How come you don't call back?

151
00:13:22,101 --> 00:13:23,151
Girlfriend?

152
00:13:24,737 --> 00:13:26,046
Cheers, sir! Cheers!

153
00:13:26,906 --> 00:13:27,756
Just leave me alone!

154
00:13:28,074 --> 00:13:29,093
It's none of my business ! don't want to know a thing

155
00:13:29,609 --> 00:13:30,949
Go! Leave me alone!

156
00:13:36,816 --> 00:13:37,716
Law

157
00:13:38,885 --> 00:13:39,755
What do you want?

158
00:13:41,654 --> 00:13:43,024
My father just passed way

159
00:13:48,127 --> 00:13:49,827
It was his wish to inform his children...

160
00:13:51,197 --> 00:13:53,627
when something bad happened to him!

161
00:13:56,703 --> 00:13:58,343
Sorry to have bothered you!

162
00:14:20,960 --> 00:14:23,480
Stop watching TV! Eat first, Negro!

163
00:14:24,530 --> 00:14:27,660
l wonder what they have on Kwun's death

164
00:14:29,569 --> 00:14:30,468
Did you do it, Ching?

165
00:14:31,838 --> 00:14:33,448
I've got a big mouth. Had ! done it...

166
00:14:33,906 --> 00:14:34,866
.. you would've heard about it!

167
00:14:35,208 --> 00:14:36,438
Ask Wah and Gandhi

168
00:14:37,810 --> 00:14:40,650
When Kwun died, I was in Macau

169
00:14:41,314 --> 00:14:42,044
Everybody knows!

170
00:14:42,548 --> 00:14:44,478
But I bet his kids think I did it

171
00:14:45,284 --> 00:14:46,654
[ain't scared of nothing

172
00:14:47,053 --> 00:14:49,423
The eldest son's a doctor The youngest a brat

173
00:14:50,056 --> 00:14:50,846
The daughter's married for ages

174
00:14:51,224 --> 00:14:52,954
Only the middle son's running the show

175
00:14:53,726 --> 00:14:57,506
If they go too far, I'll show them!

176
00:14:58,231 --> 00:15:00,251
We failed to protect Kwun. It's our fault!

177
00:15:01,167 --> 00:15:02,747
That's enough, Uncle John

178
00:15:03,236 --> 00:15:04,665
Dad used to say

179
00:15:05,605 --> 00:15:07,825
What goes around comes around

180
00:15:09,075 --> 00:15:11,765
It came later than expected already

181
00:15:13,846 --> 00:15:15,926
Wah, Ching, Negro and Gandhi

182
00:15:16,749 --> 00:15:18,969
Guess what those four are thinking?

183
00:15:23,589 --> 00:15:25,369
Thank you. Thank you all!

184
00:15:28,161 --> 00:15:30,851
How's mom doing, sis?

185
00:15:31,864 --> 00:15:33,974
She's fine. Been sleeping

186
00:15:34,700 --> 00:15:38,130
Bring some cigs to the morgue for dad

187
00:15:38,771 --> 00:15:39,670
I'll go get them

188
00:15:46,779 --> 00:15:49,359
B Team, watch Tak Shing Street

189
00:15:49,916 --> 00:15:52,376
C Team, watch the Austin Road exit...

190
00:15:53,019 --> 00:15:54,659
..Of that financial building

191
00:15:55,087 --> 00:15:56,396
It has two exits

192
00:15:56,756 --> 00:15:58,425
One on Tak Shing Street. One on Austin...

193
00:15:58,858 --> 00:15:59,497
Sorry

194
00:16:04,130 --> 00:16:04,980
Hello?

195
00:16:05,298 --> 00:16:07,468
Something this big, why didn't you call?

196
00:16:08,034 --> 00:16:10,343
l called everybody the minute it happened!

197
00:16:10,870 --> 00:16:12,540
Kwun's boys can't sit still for sure

198
00:16:13,039 --> 00:16:14,409
Shit will hit the fan tonight!

199
00:16:14,740 --> 00:16:15,820
It's the 14th already. You know that?

200
00:16:16,642 --> 00:16:19,302
The 14th. Time to pay the Ngai Family

201
00:16:21,881 --> 00:16:23,310
I'm the youngest here

202
00:16:23,716 --> 00:16:25,006
So let me be the jackass

203
00:16:25,918 --> 00:16:28,728
I'm not paying the Ngai's any more

204
00:16:29,956 --> 00:16:31,036
What do you three think?

205
00:17:24,710 --> 00:17:25,470
Inspector Wong

206
00:17:25,810 --> 00:17:26,420
What's up?

207
00:17:26,779 --> 00:17:27,919
What're your men doing outside Wah's building?

208
00:17:28,513 --> 00:17:29,154
Not a good day for chit chat

209
00:17:29,582 --> 00:17:30,072
Are you into something?

210
00:17:30,516 --> 00:17:31,856
Fine, fine. Next time

211
00:17:37,123 --> 00:17:38,413
What's the occasion?

212
00:17:39,725 --> 00:17:41,475
Come on. Where's my seat?

213
00:17:47,867 --> 00:17:50,476
Only if you're here for the food

214
00:17:51,137 --> 00:17:52,887
All other businesses have to wait

215
00:17:53,306 --> 00:17:55,266
The food. It's all about the food

216
00:18:03,616 --> 00:18:04,926
Tonight's gonna be the shit!

217
00:18:06,619 --> 00:18:08,049
Let the Big Four do their things

218
00:18:08,721 --> 00:18:09,621
We'll deal with the aftermath

219
00:18:11,223 --> 00:18:12,592
Don't let them start fighting

220
00:18:13,125 --> 00:18:14,735
Or you'll see bodies

221
00:18:15,127 --> 00:18:16,706
What? Not satisfied?

222
00:18:18,264 --> 00:18:20,873
You know the rule. Pick a card

223
00:18:22,001 --> 00:18:23,141
Okay. Higher points win

224
00:18:23,603 --> 00:18:24,213
Come on!

225
00:18:37,883 --> 00:18:40,313
There's nothing left to talk about

226
00:18:42,822 --> 00:18:43,901
What's up, Hau?

227
00:18:44,590 --> 00:18:45,439
Wah

228
00:18:45,992 --> 00:18:46,572
Nothing much

229
00:18:46,826 --> 00:18:49,226
Heard you're planning a casino in Macau

230
00:18:50,663 --> 00:18:52,393
I've got the government in my pocket

231
00:18:52,832 --> 00:18:54,412
How about a joint venture?

232
00:18:55,034 --> 00:18:56,374
Uncle Kwun's dead

233
00:18:56,969 --> 00:18:58,079
I'm not in the mood

234
00:19:02,708 --> 00:19:03,698
lsee

235
00:19:05,044 --> 00:19:06,914
The Macau trip wasn't all business

236
00:19:08,914 --> 00:19:11,494
I know you had fun with Gandhi's wife

237
00:19:38,878 --> 00:19:41,568
Sorry, but I can't let go of my casino in Macau

238
00:19:42,048 --> 00:19:42,838
Gotta go

239
00:20:04,003 --> 00:20:05,493
What are Sam's people doing?

240
00:20:06,772 --> 00:20:08,702
I know Wah paid up

241
00:20:10,009 --> 00:20:11,149
Don't change the subject

242
00:20:11,677 --> 00:20:13,577
Tell me something I don't know!

243
00:20:15,581 --> 00:20:16,841
Call me when you get your shit straight!

244
00:20:20,252 --> 00:20:22,712
Hau took care of Wah in ten minutes

245
00:20:23,255 --> 00:20:26,355
The Big Four are having a tough time

246
00:20:29,662 --> 00:20:31,802
Hau took out a million's worth of coke

247
00:20:47,813 --> 00:20:48,683
What?

248
00:20:49,582 --> 00:20:50,662
Mafia road block or what?

249
00:21:02,561 --> 00:21:05,721
[ don't know why Wah paid up, Hau

250
00:21:06,632 --> 00:21:07,482
But I ain't gonna negotiate

251
00:21:07,733 --> 00:21:08,812
I don't plan to negotiate, either

252
00:21:09,201 --> 00:21:10,491
Pass the phone to Negro

253
00:21:12,204 --> 00:21:13,134
Hey, Negro

254
00:21:13,706 --> 00:21:15,985
Don't know why he calls you from my hood

255
00:21:19,145 --> 00:21:20,165
What's up, Hau?

256
00:21:20,913 --> 00:21:22,753
I'm with Gandhi all the way

257
00:21:24,049 --> 00:21:26,799
He's not paying, neither will I!

258
00:21:27,953 --> 00:21:30,533
Heard you and Gandhi have been tight

259
00:21:31,090 --> 00:21:34,310
The heroin you two smuggled got robbed

260
00:21:35,227 --> 00:21:37,277
Lost several millions each, right?

261
00:21:38,798 --> 00:21:40,788
Luckily ! found the stuff in your warehouse

262
00:21:41,767 --> 00:21:43,607
Want me to hand it back to Gandhi now?

263
00:21:47,740 --> 00:21:48,730
What's he talking about?

264
00:22:03,923 --> 00:22:05,123
Among the Tsim Sha Tsui Big Fives...

265
00:22:05,691 --> 00:22:08,411
Wah and Negro paid up

266
00:22:09,662 --> 00:22:11,532
Counting Sam, that's 3 to 2

267
00:22:12,631 --> 00:22:14,711
I'm the youngest here. Gotta pay!

268
00:22:16,635 --> 00:22:18,035
See ya!

269
00:22:24,276 --> 00:22:26,296
Don't think too much. Cheers!

270
00:22:34,787 --> 00:22:35,987
Pay my share for me!

271
00:22:41,694 --> 00:22:44,303
Mr. Ngai went to eat, Inspector Wong

272
00:23:20,566 --> 00:23:22,316
A bit late for chowing, don't you think?

273
00:23:24,670 --> 00:23:27,190
My dad always came here after work

274
00:23:27,873 --> 00:23:30,363
l have to keep up the ritual

275
00:23:31,176 --> 00:23:33,346
Want to join us?

276
00:23:35,147 --> 00:23:37,456
It's your seat from now on. Must be tough

277
00:23:38,684 --> 00:23:39,884
Not at all

