560
00:58:26,737 --> 00:58:29,607
Whether to nail him or not...

561
00:58:30,741 --> 00:58:31,731
. that's up to you

562
00:59:23,693 --> 00:59:24,923
What a good show!

563
00:59:30,634 --> 00:59:31,684
You're so friggin’ photogenic

564
01:00:07,237 --> 01:00:08,497
Four years ago...

565
01:00:10,507 --> 01:00:12,377
How much did Sam's woman pay you?

566
01:00:16,847 --> 01:00:18,747
Give me another chance, Mr. Ngai

567
01:00:51,882 --> 01:00:53,932
I gave them a chance four years ago

568
01:00:54,951 --> 01:00:56,001
They didn't take it

569
01:00:58,955 --> 01:01:00,795
If l give you a chance

570
01:01:03,193 --> 01:01:04,713
Are you going to take it today?

571
01:01:19,676 --> 01:01:21,076
You've been with us for seven years now

572
01:01:22,979 --> 01:01:24,089
You're a cop

573
01:01:28,218 --> 01:01:29,508
We're the bad guys

574
01:01:31,054 --> 01:01:32,344
Time to accept our fates

575
01:01:37,594 --> 01:01:38,704
You can't blame me

576
01:01:40,063 --> 01:01:43,103
Your Inspector Wong killed my dad

577
01:04:27,564 --> 01:04:28,904
Any words from Sam?

578
01:04:31,034 --> 01:04:32,404
Sam called me

579
01:04:32,802 --> 01:04:33,792
He said he was fine

580
01:04:34,637 --> 01:04:38,147
He asked you to wait for him here

581
01:04:47,550 --> 01:04:48,600
Where're your folks?

582
01:04:50,620 --> 01:04:51,470
All emigrated

583
01:04:54,991 --> 01:04:56,041
You didn't go with them?

584
01:05:29,659 --> 01:05:30,799
Let's go, Sam! We got rid of the Thais

585
01:05:31,127 --> 01:05:32,387
Let's go!

586
01:05:34,764 --> 01:05:37,254
You know you're not going to make it

587
01:05:38,034 --> 01:05:38,884
l know

588
01:05:40,837 --> 01:05:42,587
My girl's in danger in Hong Kong

589
01:05:44,274 --> 01:05:45,703
Please help me

590
01:05:46,042 --> 01:05:47,682
Why should I?

591
01:05:48,611 --> 01:05:50,341
‘Cause I'll help you whack your boss

592
01:05:52,282 --> 01:05:54,422
I Know you want to be in charge

593
01:05:56,252 --> 01:05:57,392
Moreover

594
01:06:20,310 --> 01:06:22,390
I've been treating you as a pal

595
01:06:28,818 --> 01:06:30,368
Don't believe him, Sam! Don't!

596
01:06:31,054 --> 01:06:31,814
Get lost!

597
01:06:32,121 --> 01:06:33,581
Don't believe him! Get lost!

598
01:06:52,509 --> 01:06:53,499
Sorry, Sam

599
01:08:10,620 --> 01:08:11,549
Are you here to arrest me?

600
01:08:12,622 --> 01:08:13,912
If you're going to kill Hau

601
01:08:15,091 --> 01:08:16,081
I will

602
01:08:19,929 --> 01:08:21,038
Then there's nothing to talk about

603
01:08:25,501 --> 01:08:26,701
l spoke with my superiors

604
01:08:27,904 --> 01:08:30,014
They're with you all the way this time

605
01:08:31,506 --> 01:08:32,406
How?

606
01:08:32,742 --> 01:08:33,882
[ conspired in murder!

607
01:08:40,216 --> 01:08:42,266
Even the Brits agree that...

608
01:08:42,919 --> 01:08:44,788
..we can't let the triads break us

609
01:08:46,756 --> 01:08:49,566
The whole department's behind you

610
01:08:50,193 --> 01:08:51,453
Good enough?

611
01:08:55,264 --> 01:08:56,024
Where's your deck of cards?

612
01:09:04,607 --> 01:09:05,687
The higher points win

613
01:09:08,044 --> 01:09:10,184
Come back with me to the department

614
01:09:13,850 --> 01:09:14,780
The key!

615
01:09:16,886 --> 01:09:17,996
Forget it. l screwed up

616
01:09:18,587 --> 01:09:19,577
No need to drag everyone down with me

617
01:09:39,809 --> 01:09:41,589
We found this deck in our first outing together

618
01:09:42,045 --> 01:09:42,895
You've been keeping it all this time

619
01:09:43,546 --> 01:09:44,536
I knew that all along

620
01:09:48,718 --> 01:09:51,377
I've let you get your way in the past

621
01:09:52,121 --> 01:09:53,141
It's your turn to listen for once

622
01:09:54,557 --> 01:09:55,017
We're like brothers

623
01:09:55,291 --> 01:09:56,581
Think I'm just gonna be a spectator?

624
01:10:04,667 --> 01:10:06,537
Law's my snitch in the Ngai Family

625
01:10:08,905 --> 01:10:10,485
He hasn't contacted me for days

626
01:10:12,775 --> 01:10:13,705
Neither has Yan!

627
01:10:15,912 --> 01:10:16,872
The key!

628
01:11:03,192 --> 01:11:04,422
Help!

629
01:11:04,961 --> 01:11:06,891
Help! Get some help!

630
01:12:49,632 --> 01:12:50,772
Why did you lie to me?

631
01:12:53,035 --> 01:12:53,965
I didn't!

632
01:12:55,037 --> 01:12:56,467
Something happened to Sam!

633
01:12:57,740 --> 01:12:59,960
I told you I was a simple woman

634
01:13:00,643 --> 01:13:02,723
l have to do something for my husband

635
01:13:03,646 --> 01:13:04,606
I'm going to Thailand

636
01:13:05,781 --> 01:13:06,921
Please don't go!

637
01:13:08,784 --> 01:13:11,393
Forget it! You don't have to follow us anymore

638
01:13:13,089 --> 01:13:15,579
[ mean, I don't want you to go

639
01:13:21,497 --> 01:13:24,307
You've been with Sam for years

640
01:13:25,902 --> 01:13:27,132
Has it occurred to you...

641
01:13:29,105 --> 01:13:30,445
Maybe Sam's dead!

642
01:13:30,773 --> 01:13:31,623
What did you say?

643
01:13:32,575 --> 01:13:33,505
l can take care of you

644
01:13:39,815 --> 01:13:40,804
What're you doing?

645
01:13:41,150 --> 01:13:42,049
I don't want you to go!

646
01:13:45,187 --> 01:13:46,387
You're out of line!

647
01:13:54,597 --> 01:13:55,767
Listen up!

648
01:13:56,766 --> 01:13:58,056
I'm your boss's woman!

649
01:14:03,940 --> 01:14:05,370
Don't let me see your face again!

650
01:15:00,129 --> 01:15:01,739
She will go to the airport tonight...

651
01:15:02,131 --> 01:15:04,031
Hello? Hello?

652
01:16:30,719 --> 01:16:32,499
I killed Kwunt

653
01:16:33,622 --> 01:16:34,732
Aman treats me well

654
01:16:35,091 --> 01:16:36,351
I'd do anything

655
01:17:20,936 --> 01:17:23,335
Time

656
01:17:25,040 --> 01:17:27,730
Year: 1997

657
01:17:29,178 --> 01:17:31,638
File number 103142

658
01:17:32,081 --> 01:17:34,801
About Inspector Wong conspiring in murder

659
01:17:35,784 --> 01:17:39,263
This is the 11th internal hearing

660
01:17:40,589 --> 01:17:41,669
Inspector Wong

661
01:17:42,224 --> 01:17:43,484
do you have any question?

662
01:17:44,627 --> 01:17:45,617
No...

663
01:17:46,028 --> 01:17:46,958
No

664
01:17:47,730 --> 01:17:50,450
An inspector should possess leadership skills

665
01:17:51,033 --> 01:17:51,583
Mr. Lau

666
01:17:51,901 --> 01:17:53,101
you joined as a police constable

667
01:17:53,702 --> 01:17:54,722
Could you tell the promotion board

668
01:17:55,204 --> 01:17:56,784
why you deserve to be promoted?

669
01:17:57,206 --> 01:17:58,136
Of course

670
01:17:58,641 --> 01:18:01,300
On April 11, 1995...

671
01:18:02,044 --> 01:18:04,504
The department received this tape

672
01:18:05,614 --> 01:18:08,393
Accusing you of conspiring in a murder

673
01:18:09,051 --> 01:18:09,981
l confess, sir

674
01:18:10,553 --> 01:18:11,633
It's already 1997

675
01:18:12,221 --> 01:18:13,450
Before the 1st of July

676
01:18:13,956 --> 01:18:15,386
If we don't receive your PO assessment report

677
01:18:15,958 --> 01:18:17,038
Do you still think you can be promoted?

678
01:18:17,593 --> 01:18:18,793
In Chinese, there is a saying

679
01:18:19,228 --> 01:18:21,278
With a new king come new followers

680
01:18:21,797 --> 01:18:24,727
So, I guess we will have to start all over again

681
01:18:25,768 --> 01:18:27,348
What happened to you?

682
01:18:29,905 --> 01:18:31,134
If I told you...

683
01:18:31,907 --> 01:18:34,597
..that the evidence couldn't stand

684
01:18:36,579 --> 01:18:37,839
would you like to start over?

685
01:18:41,050 --> 01:18:43,890
I'm sorry. I broke the law

686
01:18:44,920 --> 01:18:47,820
What do you think of the police force's
morale after 1997?

687
01:18:48,691 --> 01:18:50,391
Chinese people are sentimental

688
01:18:50,960 --> 01:18:53,240
I hope the law will continue to back me up

689
01:18:53,696 --> 01:18:57,296
But, I strongly believe in myself, sir!

690
01:18:58,100 --> 01:18:59,620
I'm grateful to all of you

691
01:19:01,670 --> 01:19:04,450
But I've got no confidence left. I lost!

692
01:19:05,107 --> 01:19:06,337
What about Luk then?

693
01:19:07,610 --> 01:19:09,599
Can you face him if you give up now?

694
01:19:10,879 --> 01:19:13,659
The war's not over

695
01:19:15,184 --> 01:19:18,554
We all want a closure to this incident

696
01:19:20,923 --> 01:19:24,583
Hong Kong is not run by the Ngai Family

697
01:19:30,866 --> 01:19:32,736
Here's a file from the Interpol

698
01:19:33,636 --> 01:19:34,626
Read it before your make up your mind

699
01:19:57,660 --> 01:19:59,389
Ever been to a funeral in Thailand?

700
01:20:02,564 --> 01:20:03,584
A few months ago...

701
01:20:04,733 --> 01:20:06,483
[had one for my wife

702
01:20:08,570 --> 01:20:12,230
The monks chanted for three full days

703
01:20:15,878 --> 01:20:19,388
I didn't shed a single tear

704
01:20:23,085 --> 01:20:24,515
On the day of the burial...

705
01:20:26,755 --> 01:20:30,595
.. they left the casket in the living room

706
01:20:32,695 --> 01:20:33,924
l was mad

707
01:20:34,697 --> 01:20:35,807
l wanted to beat them up

708
01:20:38,300 --> 01:20:39,910
The monk told me

709
01:20:42,871 --> 01:20:44,541
it's a tradition in Thailand

710
01:20:46,942 --> 01:20:48,372
The deceased...

711
01:20:49,712 --> 01:20:51,352
As long as we keep her company...

712
01:20:52,748 --> 01:20:54,058
for a little while longer

713
01:20:56,685 --> 01:20:58,325
she can attain eternal peace

714
01:21:02,958 --> 01:21:04,447
But I asked the monk

715
01:21:08,297 --> 01:21:10,376
what if my wife was not in the coffin?

716
01:21:12,634 --> 01:21:14,364
Could she still attain eternal peace?

717
01:21:21,844 --> 01:21:23,984
Sorry about your wife

718
01:21:31,053 --> 01:21:32,833
The monk placed his hand here

719
01:21:35,224 --> 01:21:36,974
He said, "No problem

720
01:21:39,261 --> 01:21:41,721
Your wife's here."

721
01:21:48,003 --> 01:21:49,523
And here's exactly...

722
01:21:52,274 --> 01:21:54,324
..where the Thais shot me!

723
01:21:59,148 --> 01:22:00,878
So I told myself

724
01:22:07,656 --> 01:22:09,526
I've passed the point of no return

725
01:22:14,797 --> 01:22:18,717
Testifying against Hau could be dangerous

726
01:22:23,972 --> 01:22:26,522
I believe in you. You're so handsome

727
01:22:30,746 --> 01:22:33,496
Haven't heard that for ages. Thanks

728
01:22:36,752 --> 01:22:37,862
What's your plan?

729
01:22:40,956 --> 01:22:42,536
Just trying to do my best

730
01:22:43,125 --> 01:22:44,935
No big deal. It's my job

731
01:22:46,962 --> 01:22:49,332
I'll leave Hong Kong when it's all over

732
01:23:18,293 --> 01:23:19,603
You've changed

733
01:23:25,167 --> 01:23:26,067
Baby

734
01:24:12,848 --> 01:24:14,338
You diluted the coke, didn't you?

735
01:24:17,953 --> 01:24:19,003
Got anything to say?

736
01:24:33,835 --> 01:24:34,855
Take it all then!

737
01:24:40,876 --> 01:24:42,716
Don't go too far, Yan

738
01:24:43,145 --> 01:24:44,895
It'd break the boys' morale

739
01:24:49,217 --> 01:24:50,887
Mr. Ngai asked me to be in charge here

740
01:24:52,821 --> 01:24:54,661
Don't like it? Drive him to the hospital!

741
01:25:10,572 --> 01:25:11,802
No matter what

742
01:25:12,174 --> 01:25:13,514
they're elders after all

743
01:25:15,143 --> 01:25:16,923
You've got lots to learn from them

744
01:25:19,581 --> 01:25:21,721
Uncle John will retire in a few years

745
01:25:25,087 --> 01:25:26,077
You know what I mean?

746
01:25:28,156 --> 01:25:29,966
I don't need any hiccups now

747
01:25:34,129 --> 01:25:36,909
The Labor Athletic Association has a formal...

748
01:25:38,000 --> 01:25:40,340
.. for us Political Consultative candidates

749
01:25:42,004 --> 01:25:43,524
If everything works out

750
01:25:45,040 --> 01:25:46,970
our family will no longer live in shadows

751
01:26:14,736 --> 01:26:15,556
Mr. Cheung

752
01:26:15,871 --> 01:26:16,601
Mr. Ngai

753
01:26:17,339 --> 01:26:18,769
How are you? Good. Good

754
01:26:19,174 --> 01:26:20,754
When Solicitor Hung mentioned you

755
01:26:21,309 --> 01:26:22,569
I didn't believe him

756
01:26:23,145 --> 01:26:25,775
You're amazingly young, Mr. Ngai

757
01:26:26,615 --> 01:26:27,465
What's your Zodiac?

758
01:26:28,884 --> 01:26:29,494
Ox

759
01:26:29,785 --> 01:26:30,635
The Year of the Ox

760
01:26:31,219 --> 01:26:32,829
Ox's good

761
01:26:33,488 --> 01:26:36,238
Director Chan likes young people

762
01:26:36,825 --> 01:26:38,465
I'll introduce you later. Thanks

763
01:26:38,894 --> 01:26:39,654
Really?

764
01:26:42,130 --> 01:26:45,790
Director Chan said he hated the triads

765
01:26:52,607 --> 01:26:53,977
That's right, SP Leung

766
01:26:54,876 --> 01:26:57,806
Mr. Ngai's been invited to consult the police

767
01:26:58,647 --> 01:27:00,577
Really? Congratulations!

768
01:27:01,083 --> 01:27:02,513
Where do you golf these days, Chan?

769
01:27:03,051 --> 01:27:03,571
Zhong Shan Onsen

770
01:27:03,919 --> 01:27:05,789
What's your handicap these days?

771
01:27:06,588 --> 01:27:08,077
How are you? My name's Ngai...

772
01:27:18,600 --> 01:27:19,650
Mr. Ngai Wing-Hau

773
01:27:23,705 --> 01:27:24,755
I'm Mr. Ngai's solicitor

774
01:27:25,140 --> 01:27:27,420
Tonight's a celebration for HK's hand-over

775
01:27:27,943 --> 01:27:29,343
All other businesses can wait

776
01:27:29,678 --> 01:27:30,728
What if l say no?

777
01:27:31,279 --> 01:27:32,509
Got any problem with that?

778
01:27:36,084 --> 01:27:36,934
Mr. Ngai

779
01:27:37,519 --> 01:27:37,779
You're a suspect

780
01:27:38,086 --> 01:27:40,426
in several murder cases in 1995

781
01:27:42,090 --> 01:27:43,400
You're under arrest

782
01:27:43,959 --> 01:27:44,949
This is your arrest warrant

783
01:27:45,794 --> 01:27:46,784
Everything you say

784
01:27:47,129 --> 01:27:48,499
will be recorded...

785
01:27:48,964 --> 01:27:50,484
and could be used as evidence against you

786
01:27:51,032 --> 01:27:51,962
Do you have any question?

787
01:27:52,834 --> 01:27:53,704
No

788
01:28:07,716 --> 01:28:08,916
I looked through their files

789
01:28:09,217 --> 01:28:10,647
The murder charges won't stand

790
01:28:11,620 --> 01:28:13,790
But your being a triad boss...

791
01:28:14,623 --> 01:28:15,763
That one will stick

792
01:28:17,092 --> 01:28:19,612
The unions and the political parties called

793
01:28:20,128 --> 01:28:21,938
They want to withdraw their invitations

794
01:28:25,600 --> 01:28:26,940
Words from the HK and Macau Affairs Office

795
01:28:27,903 --> 01:28:29,773
They have revoked your candidacy

796
01:28:30,572 --> 01:28:32,532
Call Beijing. Get some friends to help

797
01:28:33,175 --> 01:28:34,025
Let me try

798
01:28:34,576 --> 01:28:35,216
Forget it

799
01:28:35,844 --> 01:28:37,594
They even found a dead man to testify against you

800
01:28:38,580 --> 01:28:40,720
Everyone knows how loyal Sam was to you

801
01:28:41,550 --> 01:28:43,300
Now he's the prosecution's witness It's over

802
01:28:44,586 --> 01:28:45,846
Sorry. Can't help you

803
01:28:46,922 --> 01:28:48,352
You said there'd be no problem!

804
01:28:49,090 --> 01:28:50,670
Everyone's watching how we will react

805
01:28:51,092 --> 01:28:52,382
What're you going to do?

806
01:28:52,994 --> 01:28:53,954
What can I do?

807
01:28:54,496 --> 01:28:55,136
Threaten the government?

808
01:28:55,597 --> 01:28:56,797
Don't take it the wrong way

809
01:28:57,499 --> 01:28:58,898
We're all in the same boat

810
01:28:59,601 --> 01:29:00,451
Time for me to get off then

811
01:29:01,603 --> 01:29:03,653
I'm just a lawyer. Not one of you

812
01:29:04,606 --> 01:29:06,856
I don't intend to sink with you. Sorry

813
01:29:18,520 --> 01:29:19,370
Yes

814
01:29:20,689 --> 01:29:23,149
Sam has a wife and a daughter are in Thailand!

815
01:29:25,126 --> 01:29:26,436
It's your call

816
01:29:34,135 --> 01:29:34,985
Sis

817
01:29:36,705 --> 01:29:38,755
You and the brothers should take mom...

818
01:29:39,507 --> 01:29:41,317
... and go to Hawaii for a while

819
01:29:43,612 --> 01:29:46,162
Okay. Haven't been there for a while

820
01:29:56,558 --> 01:29:57,698
Are you going to be all right?

821
01:29:58,059 --> 01:29:59,079
I'll be fine

822
01:30:00,629 --> 01:30:02,439
Sorry I can't help the family

823
01:30:03,131 --> 01:30:03,771
The key thing now is you turn out okay

824
01:30:03,999 --> 01:30:05,369
Don't be silly. We're a family!

825
01:30:06,668 --> 01:30:07,808
Take care of mom!

826
01:30:08,670 --> 01:30:10,400
Don't worry. Leave it to us three

827
01:30:22,584 --> 01:30:25,244
Even with my testimony

828
01:30:27,255 --> 01:30:29,275
Hau will only get a couple years

829
01:30:31,126 --> 01:30:32,386
It's true

830
01:30:32,694 --> 01:30:35,274
He'll have to whack you to get life

831
01:30:43,972 --> 01:30:45,022
l have to thank you

832
01:30:46,041 --> 01:30:47,031
Without you

833
01:30:47,876 --> 01:30:49,276
l could never have come back

834
01:30:52,714 --> 01:30:54,614
Save it! I'm busy these days

835
01:30:55,083 --> 01:30:57,333
Anything you need, ask them

836
01:30:57,786 --> 01:30:59,626
They'll protect you

837
01:31:16,638 --> 01:31:17,538
Sam!

838
01:31:21,309 --> 01:31:22,129
Thanks

839
01:31:25,046 --> 01:31:26,796
So, how's it going?

840
01:31:27,782 --> 01:31:30,392
Good. Been transferred to the CIB

841
01:31:31,152 --> 01:31:33,292
Will be Inspector-in-Training next month

842
01:31:39,794 --> 01:31:41,314
Did Mary call you...

843
01:31:42,630 --> 01:31:43,590
.. before she left...?

844
01:31:52,273 --> 01:31:54,673
Don't be too hard on yourself, Sam

845
01:32:01,483 --> 01:32:05,643
Inspector Wong said to find you if 1 needed anything

846
01:32:08,923 --> 01:32:10,063
Will you really help me?

847
01:33:24,165 --> 01:33:25,505
I thought you wouldn't come

848
01:33:28,903 --> 01:33:30,073
Why's that?

849
01:33:46,588 --> 01:33:47,197
So here we are

850
01:33:48,656 --> 01:33:49,676
It's been two years

851
01:33:51,826 --> 01:33:53,696
Because of my father's case

852
01:33:54,162 --> 01:33:55,562
you didn't dare to call me for two years?

853
01:33:56,131 --> 01:33:57,391
You couldn't face me?

854
01:34:00,301 --> 01:34:01,411
Right

855
01:34:12,080 --> 01:34:15,269
All you need to nail Hau is in the safe

856
01:34:17,585 --> 01:34:18,985
I've organized the files according to dates

857
01:34:24,125 --> 01:34:25,465
Why do you still help me?

858
01:34:34,169 --> 01:34:35,479
I'm not helping you

859
01:34:37,906 --> 01:34:39,016
I'm a cop

860
01:34:40,642 --> 01:34:42,662
l want to keep my promises to SP Luk!

861
01:34:45,880 --> 01:34:47,370
And I don't want to be a mole any more

862
01:34:49,717 --> 01:34:52,237
Two more years and I'll become the top dog

863
01:34:53,788 --> 01:34:56,338
What for? To end up in prison?

864
01:35:04,766 --> 01:35:06,316
Let's bury the past

865
01:35:07,602 --> 01:35:10,732
Just bring me back into the department

866
01:35:12,073 --> 01:35:14,213
Give me a desk

867
01:35:15,009 --> 01:35:16,059
Make sure it has a sea view

868
01:35:18,580 --> 01:35:19,980
And don't let me see your face again

869
01:35:23,751 --> 01:35:24,511
Don't worry

870
01:35:24,752 --> 01:35:25,892
You won't see me any more

871
01:35:27,488 --> 01:35:28,418
One more thing

872
01:35:30,191 --> 01:35:31,971
[ couldn't spell some of the words

873
01:35:32,660 --> 01:35:33,769
Come find me if you don't understand

874
01:35:34,829 --> 01:35:38,108
But don't mess up the order

875
01:35:38,866 --> 01:35:40,356
I'll kill you if you mess that up!

876
01:35:41,869 --> 01:35:44,239
That's great. Put me out of misery!

877
01:35:45,940 --> 01:35:47,309
You wish!

878
01:35:54,549 --> 01:35:55,689
Thank you, officer

879
01:36:59,580 --> 01:37:02,330
The trial will start in three days

880
01:37:04,085 --> 01:37:04,985
Mr. Hon

881
01:38:05,613 --> 01:38:06,463
OCTB!

882
01:38:09,617 --> 01:38:11,957
Inspector Wong! Sam's gone!

883
01:38:27,001 --> 01:38:28,871
He escaped through the kitchen

884
01:38:29,504 --> 01:38:30,704
Who was guarding the kitchen?

885
01:38:34,675 --> 01:38:35,545
Sorry, sir

886
01:38:37,245 --> 01:38:39,265
Sam'd made a call to Thailand...

887
01:38:39,747 --> 01:38:40,827
.. before he escaped

888
01:39:35,703 --> 01:39:36,693
Mr. Ngai

889
01:39:37,705 --> 01:39:38,934
What do you want from me?

890
01:39:40,875 --> 01:39:42,135
You called me

891
01:39:43,845 --> 01:39:46,625
So tell me how you can help me

892
01:39:47,215 --> 01:39:48,945
Am I right? Sit down

893
01:40:00,495 --> 01:40:01,635
Whack me!

894
01:40:04,999 --> 01:40:06,639
Kill me and it's all over!

895
01:40:07,668 --> 01:40:08,808
Why should I?

896
01:40:09,170 --> 01:40:10,750
Haven't done that kind of stuff for ages

897
01:40:14,775 --> 01:40:16,964
Everything can be negotiated

898
01:40:18,179 --> 01:40:19,639
Hong Kong's big enough for us both, Sam

899
01:40:20,047 --> 01:40:22,507
We can even be partners

900
01:40:26,821 --> 01:40:28,050
Let's forget about the past

901
01:40:44,939 --> 01:40:46,369
You will kill me

902
01:40:48,042 --> 01:40:49,592
You'll kill me tonight

903
01:41:00,788 --> 01:41:03,248
But who's gonna take care of your family?

904
01:41:21,876 --> 01:41:22,726
Just in!

905
01:41:23,010 --> 01:41:25,350
Hau has Sam's wife and daughter as hostages

906
01:41:26,614 --> 01:41:28,574
That's his Thai maid!

907
01:41:38,092 --> 01:41:40,842
l managed to stay alive all these years

908
01:41:42,930 --> 01:41:43,980
It's all because...

909
01:41:45,566 --> 01:41:46,996
... [have some good buddies in Thailand

910
01:41:54,208 --> 01:41:55,498
You want to take this call

911
01:41:58,145 --> 01:41:59,345
It's from Hawaii

912
01:42:04,485 --> 01:42:05,714
Your whole family's there

913
01:42:08,189 --> 01:42:09,449
My Thai buddies, too

914
01:42:20,935 --> 01:42:21,985
Hello! Mr Ngai

915
01:42:22,603 --> 01:42:23,183
My boss asked me

916
01:42:23,838 --> 01:42:25,447
to take good care of your family

917
01:42:37,685 --> 01:42:39,795
Daddy! Where are you?

918
01:42:45,793 --> 01:42:46,553
Mr. Ngai!

919
01:42:51,232 --> 01:42:52,132
Shut up!

920
01:42:58,305 --> 01:43:00,035
You'll whack me tonight. I told you so

921
01:43:56,163 --> 01:43:58,333
Put it down, Ngai Wing-Hau!

922
01:43:58,866 --> 01:43:59,916
Let him

923
01:44:02,169 --> 01:44:03,479
He tried to kill me once before

924
01:44:04,939 --> 01:44:06,399
Let him do it again!

925
01:44:14,615 --> 01:44:15,695
Officers

926
01:44:18,252 --> 01:44:19,682
After he shoots me...

927
01:44:21,622 --> 01:44:23,462
..it'll be your call to shoot him or not

928
01:44:30,531 --> 01:44:33,571
What goes around comes around!

929
01:46:50,771 --> 01:46:51,880
Two questions

930
01:46:55,476 --> 01:46:57,056
Did you kill his whole family?

931
01:46:59,580 --> 01:47:00,570
Of course not!

932
01:47:03,050 --> 01:47:06,210
My buddies and I were just scaring him!

933
01:47:09,089 --> 01:47:10,818
Did you expect me to kill him for you?

934
01:47:19,934 --> 01:47:21,714
Would you believe me if 1 said no?

935
01:47:22,269 --> 01:47:23,879
l expected to die here

936
01:47:25,940 --> 01:47:27,519
It was my only way

937
01:47:34,682 --> 01:47:35,581
Sorry

938
01:47:38,953 --> 01:47:40,763
Did you know how hard I worked...

939
01:47:41,689 --> 01:47:43,359
.. to collect tons of evidence...

940
01:47:44,091 --> 01:47:45,701
..to put him away for life?

941
01:48:10,050 --> 01:48:11,100
How are you?

942
01:48:11,618 --> 01:48:13,288
The Thai guy, Sam

943
01:48:18,258 --> 01:48:19,367
Paul!

944
01:48:20,728 --> 01:48:21,628
Thank you

945
01:48:21,962 --> 01:48:23,132
It's all good

946
01:48:23,897 --> 01:48:25,677
We're now partners

947
01:48:27,668 --> 01:48:29,397
Cocaine straight to HK from now on

948
01:48:30,004 --> 01:48:33,404
Should ! wrap up the Ngai episode?

949
01:48:34,074 --> 01:48:35,004
Paul...

950
01:48:36,643 --> 01:48:39,683
Maybe we shouldn't go too far

951
01:48:40,748 --> 01:48:42,388
It was pure luck that you bumped into me

952
01:48:44,485 --> 01:48:45,945
Otherwise you would've been killed

953
01:48:46,820 --> 01:48:48,400
We were destined to be partners...

954
01:48:48,922 --> 01:48:50,701
.. when my gun failed to kill you

955
01:48:51,492 --> 01:48:52,892
You can never go too far. Get it?

956
01:49:22,689 --> 01:49:25,439
The hand-over ceremony of Hong Kong...

957
01:49:26,060 --> 01:49:28,810
... commenced earlier at 11:20

958
01:49:30,297 --> 01:49:33,547
Both countries' anthems were played

959
01:49:34,968 --> 01:49:36,458
A British flag

960
01:49:36,870 --> 01:49:39,269
rose up in the hall

961
01:49:41,608 --> 01:49:42,948
The ceremony was dignified

962
01:49:43,544 --> 01:49:44,594
Yet it'd had its share of relaxed moments...

963
01:49:44,978 --> 01:49:46,728
before its commencement

964
01:49:47,815 --> 01:49:49,955
When both countries’ marching bands played

965
01:49:50,717 --> 01:49:53,237
some Chinese representatives took pictures

966
01:49:54,221 --> 01:49:55,420
Prince Charles

967
01:49:55,823 --> 01:49:59,303
and Governor Patten were smiling

968
01:50:00,828 --> 01:50:02,908
As the ceremony officially commenced

969
01:50:05,666 --> 01:50:06,656
Three British soldiers

970
01:50:07,000 --> 01:50:09,900
and three Chinese ones...

971
01:50:10,838 --> 01:50:13,447
.. marched slowly onto the podium

972
01:50:16,910 --> 01:50:18,110
The Chinese soldiers...

973
01:50:18,712 --> 01:50:21,842
displayed the PRC flag

974
01:50:24,084 --> 01:50:25,374
Following their lead...

975
01:50:25,686 --> 01:50:27,856
Three HK Royal Police officers...

976
01:50:28,589 --> 01:50:30,639
..emerged with

977
01:50:31,191 --> 01:50:33,471
three HK SAR Police officers

978
01:50:36,130 --> 01:50:39,150
The three SAR officers displayed...

979
01:50:39,766 --> 01:50:41,816
... the HKSAR flag to the honorable guests

980
01:50:43,504 --> 01:50:44,434
And now

981
01:50:44,705 --> 01:50:47,365
all the guests have risen

982
01:50:49,743 --> 01:50:51,703
It was exactly midnight

983
01:50:52,179 --> 01:50:53,789
The arrival of July 1st, 1997

984
01:50:55,015 --> 01:50:56,005
The PRC flag rose up...

985
01:50:56,517 --> 01:50:59,767
with the HKSAR flag

986
01:51:02,022 --> 01:51:04,862
marking the end of the colonial era

987
01:51:05,692 --> 01:51:07,272
It also signified the beginning...

988
01:51:07,628 --> 01:51:10,237
...of the One Country Two Systems policy

989
01:51:11,298 --> 01:51:12,788
The Hong Kong Special Administrative Region...

990
01:51:13,233 --> 01:51:15,843
... of the People's Republic of China
has been established

991
01:52:43,590 --> 01:52:45,550
Okay. It's a deal

992
01:52:46,126 --> 01:52:47,416
Come join me

993
01:52:47,861 --> 01:52:49,561
You know what kind of boss is the worst?

994
01:52:49,963 --> 01:52:51,603
The ugly boss

995
01:52:52,032 --> 01:52:54,282
Look's everything! Look how I shine!

996
01:52:59,806 --> 01:53:01,505
What's your name, miss?

997
01:53:15,656 --> 01:53:17,436
What's your name, miss?

998
01:53:21,795 --> 01:53:27,365
I'm Ma... Mary

999
01:53:28,568 --> 01:53:30,678
MAA...

1000
01:53:31,838 --> 01:53:33,478
M-A-Y...

1001
01:53:34,041 --> 01:53:35,941
M-A-R-Y

1002
01:53:39,646 --> 01:53:41,606
M-A-R-Y

1003
01:54:02,836 --> 01:54:05,386
Continuous Hell embodies 3 components:

1004
01:54:06,039 --> 01:54:08,228
Uninterrupted Time,
Unlimited Space Boundless Suffering

1005
01:54:08,909 --> 01:54:10,489
Transgressers of the Five Deadly Sins
fall into this hell forever

1006
01:54:11,011 --> 01:54:12,381
condemned to the ultimate incessant suffering

